      "description": "Comparison of simulated relative hemolysis index against in-vitro measurements from the FDA generic centrifugal pump dataset across 5 operating points. Mean RH prediction error 8.3%; all simulated RH values below unity consistent with experimental observations.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": {
