      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Wall shear stress profile validation against PIV measurements",
      "description": "Particle image velocimetry (PIV) data collected at mid-plane of the pump volute at 3 L/min and 3500 RPM. Simulated shear stress magnitude within 12% of PIV-derived values at 85% of measurement locations. Grid convergence index reported for the velocity field; no formal uncertainty propagation performed for the shear-stress-derived hemolysis sub-model output."
    },
