      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed (2.1M, 5.8M, 14.2M elements). GCI for velocity magnitude 2.3%; GCI for pressure 1.8%. Monotonic convergence confirmed. Fine-grid solution adopted for all production runs."
