      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions match simulated boundary conditions within measurement uncertainty; blood analog fluid properties documented.",
      "rationale": "In-vitro experiments used 37% glycerin-water solution matching blood viscosity at 37°C. Inlet flow rates set by calibrated Coriolis meter (±0.5%). Rotational speed verified by optical tachometer. Boundary condition fidelity confirmed."
