      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments conducted on same pump geometry under overlapping operating conditions as COU; fluid properties representative of clinical use.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump — identical geometry to COU device. Operating envelope (2–6 L/min, 2500–4500 RPM) encompasses all 5 COU flow-speed combinations. Blood analog properties calibrated to match clinical blood viscosity. Validation activities are directly applicable to the COU."
    },
    {
