      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model inputs documented with sources; sensitivity of RH to key inputs (viscosity, density, rotational speed) quantified.",
      "rationale": "Blood analog properties sourced from calibrated rheometry (±1.5% viscosity). Pump geometry from manufacturer CAD files with dimensional inspection report. Rotational speed from tachometer. One-at-a-time sensitivity analysis confirms RH most sensitive to rotational speed (±4.2% per 100 RPM); all sensitivities within design tolerance bounds."
    },
